name: Cell ETF
description: CETF is CellETF's governance token with a total issuance of 1 billion, no pre-excavation, no private placement, and no additional issuance, 100% for community incentives. 50% of the value captured by the fund agreement will be used for the repurchase and destruction of CETF, and the remaining 50% will be used to return investors, incubators and team operations and further development of the agreement.
